data.description: Custom built & meticulously maintained Lake Sherwood Estates home sits on a private wooded lot with no close neighbors & surrounded by trees & nature. Home has a flat driveway & seasonal views of the main lake. This 4 bed/3 full bath home has 2 beds on the main level. Main floor primary bedroom w/ ensuite bath & walk-in closet offers sliding door access to the deck. The Great room has soaring, vaulted ceiling, wood burning fireplace w/ blower, hardwood flooring and wall of windows showcasing the nature beyond plus sliding door access out to large deck, which is full width of the home (approx. 55'x10'). Open concept floor plan connects to dining room and kitchen for seamless entertaining. Kitchen updated w/ granite counters, stainless appliances including propane range & custom cabinets. Walk out lower level was built for entertaining with wet bar, pool table (staying w/ home), 2 large bedrooms, a full bathroom, & large laundry room/storage area. Walk out to 2nd deck off lower level.
